
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Ayomide Hambolu</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1f2933, #050816);
      color: #f9fafb;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
      padding: 2.5rem 2.2rem;
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
      max-width: 420px;
      width: 92%;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.35);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .avatar {
      width: 96px;
      height: 96px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin: 0 auto 1.2rem;
      border: 3px solid #38bdf8;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38bdf8, #22c55e);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0b1120;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      color: #cbd5f5;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.13em;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin: 1.4rem 0 0.4rem;
    }

    .about {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .links {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      margin-top: 1.2rem;
    }

    .links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      padding: 0.45rem 0.9rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      transition: all 0.18s ease;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
    }

    .links a:hover {
      background: #38bdf8;
      color: #020617;
      border-color: #38bdf8;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 1.6rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #9ca3af;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="card">
    <div class="avatar">A</div>
    <h1>Ayomide Hambolu</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Aspiring developer • Building cool things on the web</p>

    <p class="section-title">About</p>
    <p class="about">
      I enjoy learning how the web works and experimenting with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
      This is my simple personal page hosted with GitHub Pages.
    </p>

    <p class="section-title">Find me</p>
    <div class="links">
      <a href="https://github.com/Ay33415" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
      <a href="mailto:ayomidehambolu10@gmail.com">Email me</a>
      <!-- Add more links like LinkedIn, Twitter, etc. -->
    </div>

    <p class="footer">Made with ❤️ and a bit of curiosity.</p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
